*** Settings ***
Suite Setup       Create Output With Robot    ${MODIFIED OUTPUT}    ${EMPTY}    ${TEST DATA}
Suite Teardown    Remove File    ${MODIFIED OUTPUT}
Resource          modifier_resource.robot
